msgid "calibration steps:"
msgstr "校准步骤："

#: ../../source/unit/weight_i2c.rst:119 7b2e725d416244ef9e67178bfb72d283
msgid ""
"1.Reset offset(Tare). 2.Get the raw ADC value at no-load weight, this is "
"the Raw ADC of zero weight in 0g. 3.Put some weight on it, then get adc, "
"this is the load weight adc value and the gram weight you put on it."
msgstr ""
"1. 复位偏移量（Tare）。2. 在空载重量时获取原始 ADC 值，这是 0 g 零重量时的原始 ADC。3. 放上一些重量，然后获取 ADC "
"值；这就是负载重量的 ADC 值，以及你放上的重量（g）。"

